HEADWORD: Canna
<hw>Can"na</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It.]</ety> <def>A
measure of length in Italy, varying from six to seven feet. See
<er>Cane</er>, 4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Canna</ent>⟦br⟧
