==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Canna
<hw>Can"na</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a reed. See
<er>Cane</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of tropical plants,
with large leaves and often with showy flowers. The Indian shot
(<spn>Canna Indica</spn>) is found in gardens of the northern United
States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cannabene</ent>⟦br⟧
